<p>The <a href="<%- crop.url() %>"><%- crop.name %></a> you
  planted <strong>need water</strong>.  Your crops can&apos;t grow
  unless you water them!</p>

<p>Don&apos;t wait too long, or they will get <strong>parched</strong>;
  parched crops are worth less money when you eventually harvest
  them.</p>
